        {
            "id": 6244210,
            "title": "AI熱潮強心針！輝達財測驚豔 台積電ADR盤後漲逾3% 美股期指升",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>人工智慧 (AI) 晶片龍頭輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 周三 (19 日) 公布優於市場預期的營收預測，為 AI 熱潮注入強心針，科技股群起反攻，超微、美光、台積電 ADR 都跳漲超過 3%，美股期指聞訊走高。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6244210/l/84b233ccce5fa23acd35685a19be53d3.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">AI熱潮強心針！輝達財測驚豔 台積電ADR盤後大漲逾3% 美股期指升 (圖:Shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>輝達上季營收、獲利都優於市場預期，本季營收預測也強勁，執行長黃仁勳表示，市場對 Blackwell 晶片「需求爆表」，一席話凸顯 AI 基建熱潮背後的需求仍強勁。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>最新財測強化投資人對 AI 行情的信心，一掃近期圍繞在高估值、高舉債和晶片折舊下方面的討論。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>XTB 研究主任 Kathleen Brooks 說：「這是近乎完美的財報和財務展望，。代表輝達產品的需求將持續成長，而且有能力超越市場預期。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>輝達盤後一度大漲 6.4%，該股今年來到周四收盤為止，一路上漲近 40%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股期指上揚，標普 500 期指止住四日連跌，上漲 0.7%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a> 100 指數躍升 1.2%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>期指漲 0.2%，為亞洲股市周四開盤帶來好氣象。美元走高，各天期美債殖利率普遍下滑。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>AI 概念股報以掌聲，超微 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>) 漲 3.5%、台積電 ADR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>)漲 3.2%，美光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>) 攀升 3.4%，博通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>) 漲 2.4%，最近股價特別疲弱的 CoreWeave(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRWV:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRWV\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRWV-US</a>)大漲 7.7%，甲骨文 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ORCL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ORCL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ORCL-US</a>) 升 2.5%，Palantir(PTLR-US)彈 3.6%，超大雲端業者 Alphabet(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)、亞馬遜 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>) 都漲約 1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Vital Knowledge 指出，這份財報「應能讓懷疑者安靜下來，並有助於為年底行情鋪路」。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Hargreaves Lansdown 則表示，這份結果證實輝達的估值合理性，「AI 產業中確實有一些領域的估值需要稍作休息，但輝達並不在其中。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
